                      Last Places West Africa has its  operations base in Cotonou, Benin, and it is no coincidence. Benin is for us  one of the most exciting and interesting destinations in Africa. Of very  affordable dimensions, Benin has a little bit of everything and a unique essence,  Voodoo and the aesthetics and environment that surrounds this philosophy of  life. We have been operating in Benin since 1996, have become good connoisseurs  of this destination we like to share with all our partners.</p>
                    <p><strong>Last Places West Africa recommends:</strong><br>
